.com/article/4720212-united-airlines-ability-to-generate-strong-returns\">we last recommended it 2-months ago</a>, going up more than 84% versus 9% for the broader market. That strength, though, combined with recent news in the market from other airlines, presents</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1494117341/image_1494117341.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741611-united-airlines-stock-cautious-valuation-after-market-outperformance-rating-downgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 03:48:40"}, {"id": "4741610", "title": "Acadia Realty Trust: Improving Balance Sheet At An Extreme Valuation", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1765691374/image_1765691374.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Shopping cart filled with christmas gifts\" data-id=\"1765691374\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1765691374/image_1765691374.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1765691374/image_1765691374.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1765691374/image_1765691374.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1765691374/image_1765691374.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1765691374/image_1765691374.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1765691374/image_1765691374.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1765691374/image_1765691374.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1765691374/image_1765691374.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">J Studios/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Investors who bought Acadia Realty Trust (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AKR\" title=\"Acadia Realty Trust\">AKR</a></span>) back in November 2023 enjoyed more than 74% in total returns, from which roughly 69% has come in the form of pure price appreciation. The stock is currently pushing towards</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1765691374/image_1765691374.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741610-acadia-realty-trust-improving-balance-sheet-at-an-extreme-valuation", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 03:40:13"}, {"id": "4741607", "title": "Workday: Lower Growth Expectation, But Upside Is Still Attractive", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148703154/image_2148703154.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Business persons on meeting in the office.\" data-id=\"2148703154\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"912px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148703154/image_2148703154.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148703154/image_2148703154.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148703154/image_2148703154.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148703154/image_2148703154.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148703154/image_2148703154.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148703154/image_21487031