 "CleanSpark, Inc. 2024 Q4 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by CleanSpark, Inc. in conjunction with their 2024 Q4 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"105994\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741608-cleanspark-inc-2024-q4-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 02:15:28"}, {"id": "4741603", "title": "Quaker Chemical: Positioning Concerns", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412857430/image_1412857430.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Glass molecular structure\" data-id=\"1412857430\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1229px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412857430/image_1412857430.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412857430/image_1412857430.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412857430/image_1412857430.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412857430/image_1412857430.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412857430/image_1412857430.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412857430/image_1412857430.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412857430/image_1412857430.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412857430/image_1412857430.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Jonathan Kitchen</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>In the summer of 2023 I believed that <strong>Quaker Chemical (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/KWR\" title=\"Quaker Chemical Corporation\">KWR</a></span>)</strong> was offering a mixed bag for investors. While I believed that more earnings upside was seen, the company has only been posting flattish earnings amidst falling sales here, due</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412857430/image_1412857430.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741603-quaker-chemical-positioning-concerns", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 02:05:47"}, {"id": "4741432", "title": "Omega Healthcare: Back To Pre-Pandemic Levels, But I Think It Consolidates (Rating Downgrade)", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Money growth\" data-id=\"1445810162\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1055px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>It\u2019s been a satisfying year for Omega Healthcare Investors (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/OHI\" title=\"Omega Healthcare Investors, Inc.\">OHI</a></span>) investors as shares have appreciated by over 30%, causing them to settle above $40 and reach their pre-pandemic levels. I remained bullish on OHI during the pandemic while shares hovered around the $30</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741432-omega-healthcare-back-to-pre-pandemic-levels-but-i-think-it-consolidates-rating-downgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 02:00:00"}, {"id": "4741601", "title": "SIGA Technologies Vs Emergent BioSolutions: Product Portfolio And Future Outlook", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1211986569/image_1211986569.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Female doctor prohibiting access to a restricted area\" data-id=\"1211986569\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"567px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1211986569/image_1211986569.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1211986569/image_1211986569.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1211986569/image_1211986569.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads